amend_motion

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
amend_motion -  This method adds an amendment to the new rule/amendment/whatever, this rewrites the text of the ammendment of whatever it is.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int amend_motion(string area,
int id,
string amend_text,
string amender)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area the amendmend is to go in
%^BOLD%^id%^RESET%^ - the rule update id
%^BOLD%^amendmend%^RESET%^ - the amendmend to make
%^BOLD%^amendmender%^RESET%^ - the person amendmending
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/inherit/player_council.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds an amendment to the new rule/amendment/whatever, this
rewrites the text of the ammendment of whatever it is.
.EP

